What is an API?

What is a REST API? (Twitter, Google etc. they all use it)
    Just like a website. You make a call from client to a server and get data back with the HTTP protocol.

Go to Facebook and replace www with graph.
Add: ?fields=id,names,likes

Google maps: maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json does not work! Why? Missing parameters.
http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json?address=Copenhagen

